data.description: Indulge in over 1800 square feet of living space within this impeccably remodeled three-bedroom, two-bathroom home, perfectly situated just south of Lake Charles. Step into in the expansive open living area, adorned with new paint, flooring, and sheetrock that breathe fresh life into every corner. The  split floorplan offers privacy, while the upgraded fixtures and appliances enhance both style and functionality. Beyond the interior, step onto over half an acre of an expansive deep lot, a serene retreat with no rear neighbor. The newly installed solar panels on the roof contribute to energy efficiency, ensuring a home that's both modern and environmentally conscious. A large two-car garage provides ample space for vehicles and storage. Located on a quiet dead-end street with no HOA requirements, this residence epitomizes Southern comfort and modern convenience just minutes from city limits. Schedule your showing today!
